{"tid":867812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：裸男闖機舖「我似蠟筆小新」","createTime":"2018-10-19T03:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T04:23:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d883ad24b50e688488da53465970a2231726c6","tid":867812,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181019/20525795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F20525795&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0e57b3c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F20525795&h=9bab5b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181019/20525795</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月19日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：裸男闖機舖「我似蠟筆小新」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181019/large/a1603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181019%2Flarge%2Fa1603a.gif&h=7fad34f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子赤裸跑入遊戲機中心，警員接報到場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俗稱大馬路嘅青山公路元朗段，同大棠路交界一間銀行外面，前晚8點幾有一個男人突然當街除晒衫褲鞋襪，連埋手機耳筒全部丟喺地下，佢喺條街企咗一陣，仲笑笑口咁，途人都望住佢，有人偷笑，有人攞手機出嚟影，裸男之後跑咗大概30米走入大棠路一間喺地庫嘅遊戲機中心，當時呂先生喺度打緊機，佢話在場人士見有男人冇着衫跑落嚟就起哄。<br />\n<br />\n呂先生話個裸男當時笑笑口，在場打機嘅人整蠱佢，叫佢擺吓甫士佢又照做，裸男話自己左邊手臂有個叮噹紋身，又話自己似蠟筆小新。呂先生懷疑佢可能有不良嗜好，過度興奮搞到自己都唔知自己做緊乜。<br />\n<br />\n警察接到途人報案趕到機舖，將個男人帶入洗手間，等白車到場送佢去醫院檢查。警方話調查後相信事件唔涉及刑事成份，35歲嘅事主之後送院。警方將案列做發現懷疑精神紊亂人士處理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：躁伯真情演繹　港鐵冧檔之逼到癲"},{"pid":"f18dc4e7245b895debcafee8bee46bb693415b14","tid":867812,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89cd7fd27b3eb2805b449bcce3e4a18f6f6139a","tid":867812,"uid":5278,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔係發現傻人案"},{"pid":"64e50cbad29e04a248867b38c3422405e84bf8d5","tid":867812,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"真係幾似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b475e009c1cefc4c2673f62682cbac6dd5daa29c","tid":867812,"uid":78468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"身分證呢？"},{"pid":"27b90a9c906ca1ef464c467514d23ca3e9eafb1b","tid":867812,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"第二人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4845c2bd464d6564e1f0a87f7d0377996c284ec3","tid":867812,"uid":81355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b475e009c1cefc4c2673f62682cbac6dd5daa29c","tid":867812,"uid":78468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"身分證呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"呀sir你睇暈我全身有邊忽zip得落張身份證呢？"},{"pid":"deb6495916daf90a902007645a239b269542cce9","tid":867812,"uid":160135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4845c2bd464d6564e1f0a87f7d0377996c284ec3","tid":867812,"uid":81355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b475e009c1cefc4c2673f62682cbac6dd5daa29c","tid":867812,"uid":78468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"身分證呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"呀sir你睇暈我全身有邊忽zip得落張身份證呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"PC26324 o係街口發現一件露體狂,懷疑有輕度弱智兼阻差辦公,即刻派架車黎丫唔該"},{"pid":"3c62fdb4d05a59594accb4205a82db83c8fa2222","tid":867812,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4845c2bd464d6564e1f0a87f7d0377996c284ec3","tid":867812,"uid":81355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b475e009c1cefc4c2673f62682cbac6dd5daa29c","tid":867812,"uid